room_title: Escape room "Prison Break - Walk the Mile" by Odyssey Escape Game in Chicago

room_description: Your execution is set for tomorrow morning. You've tried everything to prove your innocence, but the documents backing up your alibi disappeared right before the deciding court session. You suspect a vengeful prison warren may have been behind it. Now the last chance for your freedom is to distract the guards and try to locate your files in the security office.
